## Redis Configuration

### Cache Setup
```bash
# Configure Redis memory settings
ansible {{ region }}_cache -m lineinfile -a "
  dest=/etc/redis/redis.conf
  regexp='^maxmemory'
  line='maxmemory {{ cache_size | default('2gb') }}'
"

# Configure eviction policy
ansible {{ region }}_cache -m lineinfile -a "
  dest=/etc/redis/redis.conf
  regexp='^maxmemory-policy'
  line='maxmemory-policy {{ eviction_policy | default('allkeys-lru') }}'
"

# Restart Redis
ansible {{ region }}_cache -m systemd -a "name=redis state=restarted"
```

### Application Cache Integration
```bash
# Update application cache configuration
ansible {{ region }}_app -m template -a "
  src=cache-config.j2
  dest=/opt/app/config/cache.conf
"
```

